room_title: Escape room "Cuban Crisis" by Escapology Austin in Austin
review: The experience is in the details. What makes this escape experience outstanding is the multiple types of puzzles, challenges and environments. This time I went with my 15-year-old daughter and her friend but next time we will bring the whole family. We saved the world from Nuclear Annihilation. Will you?

room_title: Escape room "Cuban Crisis" by Escapology Austin in Austin
review: My group and I were able to walk in and play with no reservations or wait. We played the Nuclear room and it was fun and interactive. A great afternoon!

room_title: Escape room "Cuban Crisis" by Escapology Austin in Austin
review: We had a blast. Went with out of town friends and had a great time. I highly recommend Nuclear Annihilation game.
